casebody.data:
RESIDENTS FOR A BETTER COMMUNITY & Barbara Hinkson Craig, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
WCI COMMUNITIES, INC., et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-5005 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 26, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellees' motion to dismiss is granted, and this appeal is dismissed as from a nonfinal, nonappealable order. See Mcllveen v. Mcllveen, 644 So. 2d 612 , 612 (Fla. 2d DCA1994).

NORTHCUTT, BLACK, and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
